high_descs: Turn left and walk to the table in the middle of the room.
Pick up the blue candle holder that is closest.
Turn around and face the couch chairs so that the lamp is on the left.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp while holding the blue candle holder.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the coffee table, go to the right side of the coffee table and face it long ways.
Pick up the blue vase closer to you on the table.
Turn around and bring the vase to the lamp in the corner.
Turn on the tall lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Examine a blue vase by the light of the tall lamp.

high_descs: walk through the living room, face the coffee table on the right side
pick up the blue disk on the left of the table
turn around, walk to the two beige chairs underneath a picture and next to a floor lamp
anns.task_desc: turn on a floor lamp with a blue disk in hand
